LIEN AGENT NOTICE

For any improvements costing $30,000 or more to real property, the property owner must designate a lien agent before work begins. The lien agent is:

Lien Agent Name: {{lien_agent_name}}
Lien Agent Address: {{lien_agent_address}}
Lien Agent Contact: {{lien_agent_contact}}

Subcontractors and suppliers must notify the lien agent of their involvement in the project to preserve their lien rights. As the property owner, you should obtain written lien waivers from all parties before making final payment.

NOTICE OF RIGHT TO CANCEL

You have the right under federal law to cancel this transaction within three business days of signing. To cancel, notify us in writing at:
{{contractor_name}}, {{contractor_address}}

